Product_name: Nulo MedalSeries Bone & Beef Broth Wet Dog & Cat Food, 2 oz., Case of 24
Product_description: Nulo MedalSeries Bone Broth is made by gently cooking high-quality beef bones for up to 10 hours to extract nourishing collagen protein and infuses ingredients like parsley, thyme and turmeric to make a wholesome broth. Simply pour over your dog or cat's next kibble or freeze-dried meal to add nourishment and flavor.
Nutritions: Crude Protein (Min) 0.50%, Crude Fat (Min) 0.10%, Crude Fiber (Max) 0.30%, Moisture (Max) 99.0%.
Ingredients: Filtered Water, Beef Bones, Apple Cider Vinegar, Kale, Carrots, Parsley, Basil, Thyme, Lemon Juice, Turmeric.
